HEADWORD: Pseudohalter
<hw>Pseu`do*hal"ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>;
<plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>Pseudohalteres</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu>
<ety>[NL. See <er>Pseudo-</er>, and <er>Halteres</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>One of the rudimentary front wings of certain
insects (<gen>Stylops</gen>). They resemble the halteres, or rudimentary
hind wings, of Diptera.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

